<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>“幸亏没砸到路人，必须严惩”</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>“不要再让醉酒成为借口了”</span></strong><strong><span></span></strong></span></p>
